  <brief_title>Juvenile Rheumatoid Arthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Multi-center, Blinded, Placebo-controlled Study With an Open-label Run-in Period to Evaluate the Efficacy, Safety, and Pharmacokinetics of Daily, Single, Subcutaneous Injections of r-metHuIL-1ra (Anakinra) in Polyarticular-Course Juvenile Rheumatoid Arthritis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
