  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety of anakinra in patients with
      Polyarticular-Course Juvenile Rheumatoid Arthritis, a form of rheumatoid arthritis affecting
      children.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
